<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Order Booking</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the order booking for investigation of the out patient. This screen will be used for maintaining order booking for investigations. This screen will contain information about Clinical notes, prescribed by and test name.
<br />
<hr /><br />
<img src="images/Lab_orderbooking.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Service No:</span><br />
    User can write Service no., based on service no. a list of Patient name will appear. It can't remain blank.
<br />
<span class="title">Patient Name: </span> <br />
    User can select patient name from the list, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Visit No: </span> 
    <br />Based on selection Patient Name latest visit id will display, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Order No: </span> 
    <br />It is system generated number, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Order Date: </span> 
    <br />It is system generated date, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Order Time:</span> 
    <br />It is system generated time, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Service No: </span> 
    <br />It is patient service no, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">HIN No: </span> 
    <br />It is patient HIN No, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Visit No: </span> 
    <br />It is patient visit no, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Patient Name: </span> 
    <br />It is patient name, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Sex: </span> 
    <br />It is patient sex, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Age: </span> 
    <br />It is patient age, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Martial Status: </span> 
    <br />It is patient martial status, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Religion:</span> 
    <br />It is patient religion, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Test Type: </span> 
    <br />User can select test type, it contains regular and urgent, Default value is regular, it can't remain blank.

<br />
    <span class="title">Clinical Notes: </span> 
    <br />User can write patient clinical notes, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Prescribed by: </span> 
    <br />
    User can select the Doctors from the given list,  it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Test Name: </span> 
    <br />User can order test details, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Template: </span> 
    <br />User can create his own Department wise templates.
<br />
    <span class="title">Provisional Diagnosis: </span> 
    <br />
    It will be auto generated.
<br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on submit button user can save the data.
<br />
    <span class="title">Reset (Button): </span> 
    <br />Clicking on reset button, will clear the current or existing data.
</p>
